snippet.textDisplay: Sve ce jednom proci... Nasi datumi na kalendaru, nase pjesme koje smo slusali u sitne sate sakrivajuci se od svih, i sve uspomene koje smo skupljali jos od skolskih hodnika... Proci ce vrijeme, zaboravit cu broj tvog mobitela, crte tvog lica, osmijeh... Samo nikad onaj osjecaj koji sam imao samo s tobom, koji se probudi svaki put kad te izmislim u slucajnoj prolaznici koja ima nesto tvoje. 🥀

snippet.textDisplay:
Lyrics:

Ko mi tebe uze? Ko mi tebe posla?
Ko provocira naše suze svaki put kad bi došla?
Meni mozak brani da se tebi predam,
tvoja pojava me hrani, al se ipak ne dam.
I samo te gledam, osećaj je izvanredan
i toj drogi biću predan makar ost'o čedan.

Ref:
Lutko ja sam rešen da večno s tobom plešem x2

Pogled tvoj me srami, al' mi strašno godi,
miris tvoj me mami, dodir tvoj me vodi.
Ti si cilj mog lutanja i predmet pobude,
razlog mog drhtanja, boja moje požude.
I dok tonem u san u mraku čujem tvoj glas,
na jastuku stiskam tvoj dlan, orkestar svira za nas.

Ref:
Lutko ja sam rešen da večno s tobom plešem x4

snippet.textDisplay:
Such a beautiful song, someone from the past dedicated this song to me and i still listen to it :) 

Here are the English Lyrics, for people like me who don't understand the language

Who took you from me
Who sent you to me
who provokes our tears
every time you come
 
My brain doesn't let me
to give myself to you
your appearance feeds me
but I still restrain
 
And I just look at you
feeling is outstanding
and to that drug I will be devoted
even if I remain chaste
 
Reference. 2x
Baby, I'm resolved
to dance with you forever
 
The look in your eyes makes me embarrassed
but it feels so good
Your scent lures me
your touch is taking me
 
You are the goal of my wandering
and the subject of motivation
the reason for my trembling
color of my lust
 
And while I slowly falling asleep
in the dark I hear your voice
on the pillow I squeeze your palm
and orchestra plays to us...
